original_title: Netanyahu a ‘war hero’ – Trump — RT World News
article_summary: US officials Vance, Rubio, and Witkoff are leading efforts to arrange a meeting between Russian President Vladimir Putin and Ukraine's Vladimir Zelensky, as the White House aims to expedite the next phase of the peace process. Meanwhile, a Western-trained Ukrainian sabotage group was busted by Russian law enforcement, planning terrorist attacks against Russian infrastructure.</s>
